docs.abstract: Genetic disease risk screening is becoming a popular employee benefit. But the tests may not be all that beneficial for the general population, experts say.
docs.snippet: Genetic disease risk screening is becoming a popular employee benefit. But the tests may not be all that beneficial for the general population, experts say.
docs.lead_paragraph: Levi Strauss & Company introduced a novel benefit for employees at its San Francisco headquarters last fall: free genetic screening to assess their hereditary risks for certain cancers and high cholesterol.

headline.main: Employees Jump at Genetic Testing. Is That a Good Thing?

docs.abstract: As Facebook prepares to hold its annual developer conference this week, many businesses are objecting to how the company has limited their access to its users’ information.
docs.snippet: As Facebook prepares to hold its annual developer conference this week, many businesses are objecting to how the company has limited their access to its users’ information.
docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — For years, Cubeyou made a business out of personal data on Facebook. The company had unfettered access to Facebook users’ information, which it gathered up through quizzes and later sold as reports to clients.

headline.main: Facebook’s Privacy Changes Leave Developers Steaming
headline.print_headline: Facebook Tightens Privacy Policy, and App Makers Are Feeling the Pinch

docs.abstract: Company officials played down the extent of the incident. Last year, the WannaCry malware struck thousands of computer systems around the world.
docs.snippet: Company officials played down the extent of the incident. Last year, the WannaCry malware struck thousands of computer systems around the world.
docs.lead_paragraph: Boeing said on Wednesday that it was hit by a cyberattack that some Boeing executives identified as the same WannaCry computer virus that struck thousands of computer systems in more than 70 countries around the world last year.

headline.main: Boeing Possibly Hit by ‘WannaCry’ Malware Attack
headline.print_headline: Malware, Possibly ‘WannaCry,’ Strikes Computers at Boeing

docs.abstract: Many streaming video providers offer movies and television shows with embedded text descriptions for those who cannot hear the words being spoken.
docs.snippet: Many streaming video providers offer movies and television shows with embedded text descriptions for those who cannot hear the words being spoken.
docs.lead_paragraph: Q. How do I find English-language content with English-language subtitles? I am hard of hearing and lots of content, principally movies, will have subtitles in every language under the sun, except English.
